  <Expressions>
    <Expression enabled="true" ident="KeyStreaming">
      <expr><![CDATA[if ((Translate(Connection_Version, true, "GS_VERSION", "VERSION") == "8411")
		|| (String2Integer(Translate(Connection_Version, true, "GS_VERSION", "VERSION")) >= 8601))
	if (Strcmp(GetRuntimeParameter("SecurityData"), "Y"))
		if (Strcmp(Translate(Config_Options, true, "KEYSTREAM1", "ISIN"), "Y"))
			if (OneHasValue(ID_BB_UNIQUE))
				return ID_BB_UNIQUE;
			else if (OneHasValue(ID_BB_GLOBAL))
				return ID_BB_GLOBAL;
			else if (OneHasValue(ID_ISIN))
				return ID_ISIN;
			else if (OneHasValue(ID_BB_PARENT_CO))
				return ID_BB_PARENT_CO;
			else if (OneHasValue(ID_BB_COMPANY))
				return ID_BB_COMPANY;
			else
				return "";
		else if (Strcmp(Translate(Config_Options, true, "KEYSTREAM2", "BBPARENT"), "Y"))
			if (OneHasValue(ID_BB_PARENT_CO))
				return ID_BB_PARENT_CO;
			else if (OneHasValue(ID_BB_COMPANY))
				return ID_BB_COMPANY;
			else
				return "";
		else
			return "";
	else if (Strcmp(GetRuntimeParameter("IssuerData"), "Y"))
		if (Strcmp(Translate(Config_Options, true, "KEYSTREAM2", "BBPARENT"), "Y"))
			if (OneHasValue(ID_BB_PARENT_CO))
				return ID_BB_PARENT_CO;
			else if (OneHasValue(ID_BB_COMPANY))
				return ID_BB_COMPANY;
			else
				return "";
		else
			return "";
	else
		return "";
else if (Strcmp(Translate(Config_Options, true, "KEYSTREAM1", "ISIN"), "Y"))
	if (OneHasValue(ID_BB_UNIQUE))
		return ID_BB_UNIQUE;
	else if (OneHasValue(ID_BB_GLOBAL))
		return ID_BB_GLOBAL;
	else if (OneHasValue(ID_ISIN))
		return ID_ISIN;
	else if (OneHasValue(ID_BB_PARENT_CO))
		return ID_BB_PARENT_CO;
	else if (OneHasValue(ID_BB_COMPANY))
		return ID_BB_COMPANY;
	else
		return "";
else if (Strcmp(Translate(Config_Options, true, "KEYSTREAM2", "BBPARENT"), "Y"))
	if (OneHasValue(ID_BB_PARENT_CO))
		return ID_BB_PARENT_CO;
	else if (OneHasValue(ID_BB_COMPANY))
		return ID_BB_COMPANY;
	else
		return "";
else
	return "";]]></expr>
    </Expression>
    <Expression enabled="true" ident="RecordIdentifier">
      <expr><![CDATA[if (AllHaveValue(ID_BB_UNIQUE, MARKET_SECTOR_DES))
	return Strcat(ID_BB_UNIQUE,
			Strcat(";", Strcat(MARKET_SECTOR_DES, Strcat(";", Strcat(ERRORCODE, Strcat(";", "OUT"))))));
else if (AllHaveValue(SECURITIES, MARKET_SECTOR_DES))
	return Strcat(SECURITIES,
			Strcat(";", Strcat(MARKET_SECTOR_DES, Strcat(";", Strcat(ERRORCODE, Strcat(";", "OUT"))))));
else
	return Strcat(SECURITIES, Strcat(";", Strcat(ERRORCODE, Strcat(";", "OUT"))));]]></expr>
    </Expression>
